databaseQueries.query: SELECT `name` FROM `roles` inner join `role_user` on `roles`.`id` = `role_user`.`role_id` WHERE `role_user`.`user_id` = 7 and `role_user`.`user_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'

SELECT `name` FROM `permissions` inner join `permission_user` on `permissions`.`id` = `permission_user`.`permission_id` WHERE `permission_user`.`user_id` = 7 and `permission_user`.`user_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'
SELECT `display_name` FROM `roles` inner join `role_user` on `roles`.`id` = `role_user`.`role_id` WHERE `role_user`.`user_id` = 7 and `role_user`.`user_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'
SELECT count(*) as aggregate FROM `roles` WHERE `name` = 'call_centre_admin'

SELECT `restaurant_id`, `id`, `title` FROM `menu_categories` WHERE exists (SELECT * FROM `menu_items` WHERE `menu_categories`.`id` = `menu_items`.`menu_category_id`) and `menu_categories`.`restaurant_id` in (1) ORDER BY `title` ASC
SELECT * FROM `menu_items` WHERE `menu_items`.`restaurant_id` in (1) ORDER BY `menu_category_id` ASC
SELECT * FROM `opening_hours` WHERE `opening_hours`.`restaurant_id` in (1) ORDER BY `day_id` ASC, `FROM` ASC
